All Gone Pete Tong & Tensnake Ibiza 2014 is the definitive sound of the White Isle for 2014, mixed by two of the scene's leading DJs and tastemakers. From pop-leaning house music to fierce, underground techno and everything in between, featuring two brand new and exclusive tracks; Coldplay 'Midnight' (Tong & Rogers Mix) and Tensnake 'Pressure' (Special Request Remix). This is two mixes of forward-thinking dance music of the highest order, representing yet another remarkable addition to the All Gone series
